the use of <ENAMEX TYPE="ORGANIZATION">LSC</ENAMEX> funds for those activities found elsewhere in
the
Appropriations Act. See ย<NUMEX TYPE="MONEY">งยง504</NUMEX>(a)(<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">2</ENAMEX>), (<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">3</ENAMEX>), (<ENAMEX TYPE="CONTACT_INFO">4</ENAMEX>). The restriction
