<ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">clients founders</ENAMEX> on the reality that the <ENAMEX TYPE="PER_DESC">doctors</ENAMEX> in <ENAMEX TYPE="LOCATION">Rust</ENAMEX> had a
